        [A __EGG_MAJOR_FUNCTION_OBJECT__]
    ]
    [
        [`memoize(_pfo)(a1)`]
        [`_fwd_arg_list([_const(_pfo)(fixed, _fwd_arg_list([a1], by_value))], by_value)`]
    ]
]

[heading Preconditions]
* A __FUNCTION_OBJECT__ returned from `memoize(_pfo)` must always be called with the same type arguments.
* `_typeof(a1)` is __COPY_ASSIGNABLE__, __COPY_CONSTRUCTIBLE__ and __EQUALITY_COMPARABLE__.
* `_decltype(memoize(_pfo)(a1))` is __COPY_CONSTRUCTIBLE__.
* __PRECONDITION_AS_IS__

